::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer walks out of the CR chambers, walking to the bridge of the Alliance 
base. He glances at the scanners, his eyes narrowing when he sees a bot at 
the base, obvioustly wanting to join, and another flying through the area.

DevilDuer walks out of the Alliance base, looking at Hurricane. "You wanna 
join, eh?" he says, looking the bot over, "Allright. Hey, I got a mission for 
you. I'm going to check out this one bot in the territory, you want to come? 
Oh, I'm DevilDuer, what's your name?"
